{"tid":1652193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［徵文會友］整封香港示威者對美國公民公開信點睇？","createTime":"2019-10-13T15:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T15:51:42.000Z","uid":136958,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a1f449dcfcd3437f6672feaba9424d695356fbd","tid":1652193,"uid":136958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"就趁住 <span style=\"color: red;\">聽日就係法案集會</span>連登又<span style=\"color: red;\">整咗World台</span> 冇理由放過呢個極致文宣機會 twitter好 fb 好 乜9都好<br />\n<br />\n小弟就諗咗少少 內容 歡迎屌下執下<br />\n而前言 格式 結語 <span style=\"color: red;\">甚至要translate做英文</span> 都好需要各巴絲通力合作 令到 遠在 一萬二千幾公里既美國 都可以 連成一線<br />\n<br />\n內容嚟講 小弟建議 要有幾個大方向<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">要update下 香港依家情況 我地毋忘初衷 講下正苦打壓 違反人權既野 酷刑 被自殺之類</span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">溫情 大約同美國人民一樣嚮往民主自由國度</span> <br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">最後梗係好多謝 美國唔同議員 聲援團體 廣大市民對香港示威者既支持同肯定</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">召集所有文人 中英文巴絲！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c430bf73f04465f7c0123c4bc4bcec23943d5b6c","tid":1652193,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:06:05.000Z","msg":"Need"},{"pid":"52ece50ed4660820aaf969874f0918aa99550b1e","tid":1652193,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4c68923ae309fb258049ecdd36511bd0c88ccfb","tid":1652193,"uid":136958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"推俾文人睇 <br />\n就顯示下香港人既質素<br />\n一晚入面做唔做到beautiful letter"},{"pid":"3661a502ddb7ef41889c6dc17cafc7b6d1777697","tid":1652193,"uid":136958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"推 文宣組入嚟未"},{"pid":"1a08c30622b400fa4afb3843c8c0de6475697307","tid":1652193,"uid":287015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"空氣推<br />\n希望可以呼籲到佢地罷買中國貨"},{"pid":"1024ba7b6b5fe05f4fb7df